item.title: CVE-2021-20847|2024-08-03T17:53:22.731Z -- ntt%20docomo%2C%20inc. -- wi-fi%20station%20sh-52a
item.description: Cross-site scripting vulnerability in Wi-Fi STATION SH-52A (38JP_1_11G, 38JP_1_11J, 38JP_1_11K, 38JP_1_11L, 38JP_1_26F, 38JP_1_26G, 38JP_1_26J, 38JP_2_03B, and 38JP_2_03C) allows a remote unauthenticated attacker to inject an arbitrary script via WebUI of the device.
